casebody.data:
PEOPLE of the State of Michigan, Plaintiff-Appellee,
v.
Paul J. BETTS, Jr., Defendant-Appellant. SC: 148981
COA: 319642 Supreme Court of Michigan. January 16, 2019

Order

On order of the Chief Justice, the motion of plaintiff-appellee to extend the time for filing its supplemental brief is GRANTED. The supplemental brief submitted on January 15, 2019, is accepted as timely filed.
